⸻

The Killer MVP Feature

Email → Structured Orders

Companies send purchase orders like this:

“Can you ship 500 units of SKU 201 to Dallas by next Thursday?”

Your AI converts that into structured data:

SKU: 201
Quantity: 500
Ship to: Dallas
Ship date: Thursday

Then routes it to the correct system.

This alone removes a huge amount of manual work.

⸻

