Feature 3: Exception Detection

The real cost in supply chains comes from exceptions.

Examples:
	•	shipment delay
	•	missing inventory
	•	incorrect order data
	•	wrong address
	•	damaged goods

Your AI detects them and suggests solutions.

Example:

Inventory short by 40 units

